reviews.name: "Cross Style" Magazine Rack with Shelves, Satin Nickel
reviews.reviewText: I don't have anything bad to say about this product. It's stylish, fits anywhere, and is pretty sturdy. It adds a bit of class to a situation that might not be very classy.
reviews.title: Perfect

reviews.name: "Cross Style" Magazine Rack with Shelves, Satin Nickel
reviews.reviewText: Not difficult to put together. Perfect in my very small bathroom.
reviews.title: Works well in bathroom

reviews.name: "Cross Style" Magazine Rack with Shelves, Satin Nickel
reviews.reviewText: It is slender enough to put it right between the toilet and the wall which was a hard space to fit a stand!! It was very easy to put together and quick! My 3-year-old even helped!! It fits several magazines and I also put extra toilet paper on it! Great product we also have the matching stand to go over the toilet and have had it for several years now so it will last a long time!
reviews.title: Great bathroom accessory!

reviews.name: "Cross Style" Magazine Rack with Shelves, Satin Nickel
reviews.reviewText: I tought size will be just a little different ! But still a very nice buy! We have a shower and toilet space separated / divided, so it is a nice fit for a small space to hold small items that we need in "that " area !! I like it very much
reviews.title: Nice piece for a small space !

reviews.name: "Cross Style" Magazine Rack with Shelves, Satin Nickel
reviews.reviewText: It's very easy to put together and it looks great in my bathroom. Highly recommended!
reviews.title: great value
